HEADWORD: Water meter
<hw>Wa"ter me"ter</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <def>A contrivance for measuring a
supply of water delivered or received for any purpose, as from a street
main.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

